name: Unidentified_Nautolan_musician
content:
A Nautolan female musician was popular during the Galactic War between the Galactic Republic and the reconstituted Sith Empire. Around 3637 BBY, she sought help in acquiring a pair of barbed ginxes, a species of swamp-dwelling amphibians which were banned as pets on Glee Anselm, the Mid Rim planet which was the Nautolan homeworld.
An individual associated with one of the two opposing governments had a companion of theirs devise a plan to acquire the ginxes.
The Nautolan musician was mentioned in the Crew Skill mission "A Nautolan's Best Friend," released as part of the 2014 Shadow of Revan expansion to the 2011 BioWare video game, Star Wars: The Old Republic.
